article_id:3318,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue Preventing Certain Screens from Displaying Correctly,image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>【Addendum<span class="local_date" data-local_date="1665647520"></span>】</strong></span></div><div>We have confirmed that the following operation may resolve this issue.</div><div><br>Please try it if you are experiencing this issue.<br>・Log out of your Google Play account, then log in once again<br>Thank you for your patience and understanding.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>It has come to our attention that an issue occurring since around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1665639000"></span> is preventing certain screens (such as the summoning and stamina recovery screens) from displaying correctly.<br><br>We are currently investigating this issue.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1665643020,update_time1665655139